":51},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......我们绕一下路。","id":53},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"绕路？","id":55},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"你现在要去的地方应该是......","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"安魂教堂。","id":58},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":59},{"type":"Dialog","id":60},{"type":"character","id":61},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":62},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"1.5","id":63},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.4","id":64,"musicid":1},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":65},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"萨卡兹。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":66},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我原本打算到大教堂之后，请菲亚梅塔小姐帮忙求情......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":67},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"要让高阶执行者监察也好、要让戍卫队随行也好......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":68},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"只要能确认塞茜莉亚对拉特兰是安全的......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":69},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"能不能，让塞茜莉亚，在费莉亚下葬之前，去见母亲最后一面。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":70},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"可是，萨卡兹。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":71},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"如果塞茜莉亚的父亲是萨卡兹......那塞茜莉亚就应该是萨卡兹。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":72},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"她却获得了光环......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":73},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"......我到底是不是在做梦。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":74},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"如果塞茜莉亚只是普通的“例外”......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":75},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"但她是萨卡兹......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":76},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"获得了光环的萨卡兹，怎么可能从大教堂走出来......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":77},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"就算，就算，她不会被......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":78},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"她怎么可能还能离开大教堂......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":79},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":80},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"......即使会被公证所开除，我也要试一试。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":81},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"带塞茜莉亚去安魂教堂。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":82},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"至少让她说声再见。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":83},{"type":"Subtitle","id":84},{"type":"Dialog","id":85},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":86},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":87},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":88},{"type":"Character","id":89},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g11_laterano_alley","screenadapt":"showall","id":90},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":91},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$exciting_intro","key":"$exciting_loop","volume":"0.4","id":92,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":94},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"