9},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"给我滚出来！！！！！","id":150,"figure":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":151},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":152},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":153},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":154},{"type":"Character","id":155},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving","screenadapt":"showall","id":156},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":157},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$sjoyasorrow_intro","key":"$sjoyasorrow_loop","volume":"0.4","id":158,"musicid":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":160},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#3$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"我真不明白，教宗阁下为什么对那帮“迷途者”如此......放任自流。","id":162},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"莫斯提马，你能告诉我吗，既然你们认识？","id":164},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"我可不想和你谈这个话题。","id":166},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"1","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"就这么记仇？","id":168},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"毕竟那时候我没死在那家伙手上，却差点被你杀了呢。","id":170},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"2","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"很难忘的经历。","id":172},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"1","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"这就是你在我面前一直戴着帽子的原因？不难受吗？","id":174},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"都做了这么久万国信使了。戴帽子而已。","id":176},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"2","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"和你，多一事不如少一事。","id":178},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"1","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"你在埋怨我吗，莫斯提马？","id":180},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"2","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"拉特兰始终有拉特兰要维护的东西，也总有人要在乎这些事。我无所谓。","id":182},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"1","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"莫斯提马，你可能稍微有些误解。很少有堕天使留在教廷，并不是因为教廷如何，而是因为那些堕天的萨科塔本身。","id":184},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"1","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"我的态度也许是有一点特别......莫斯提马，你以为自己就不是个怪胎吗？","id":186},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"2","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"你这么和我说话，就不怕我变成你口中那种“正常的堕天使”？","id":188},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"如果你会，就听不到我和你“这么说话”了。","id":190},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#8$2","focus":"2","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"行吧。说点实在的，什么时候把菲亚梅塔调走？","id":192},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$2","focus":"2","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"总是跟着我，对她没好处。","id":194},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$2","focus":"1","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"这句话你不和她本人说吗？","id":196},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$2","focus":"2","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"说过了，没用。","id":198},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$2","focus":"1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"我说就有用吗？","id":200},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"根据我的观察，权力的方便之处就是可以无视他人的意愿。","id":202},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"1","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"无视他人的意愿是要付出代价的......你为什么想调走菲亚梅塔，说来听听。","id":204},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"菲亚梅塔说是我的护卫，你们就不好奇我有什么需要她护卫的？","id":206},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"当然，也有人觉得她是我这个堕天使的监视者。","id":208},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"2","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"这么想的人恐怕对菲亚梅塔没有丝毫了解。","id":210},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"我不过是菲亚梅塔的饵，用来钓安多恩的。","id":212},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"1","id":213},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"她要是听见你这么说，恐怕不会很开心。","id":214},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"2","id":215},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"好吧，那我换个说法......饵是我背上这对锁与匙。","id":216},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"1","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"所以？让菲亚梅塔遂愿有什么不好吗？如果她能干掉安多恩，或者把他缉拿回大教堂，我当然乐见其成。","id":218},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"1","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"还是说，你们俩加一块也捉不到安多恩？","id":220},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"那倒不至于。只要安多恩还惦记着锁与匙，他就逃不掉。","id":222},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$2","focus":"2","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"只不过......我在想啊。","id":224},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$2","focus":"2","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"如果安多恩已经找到别的路了呢？","id":226},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#6$2","focus":"2","id":227},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"我不想见到的是，我走出来了，蕾缪安走出来了，甚至安多恩都走出来了......菲亚梅塔却还陷在八年前那个雨夜里。","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"没法和菲亚梅塔说这些。","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"也就是这种时候，我会稍微怀念一下共感的好处......","id":230},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$2","focus":"2","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"啊，忘了菲亚梅塔是黎博利。那当我没说。","id":232},{"type":"dialog","id":233},{"type":"character","id":234},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":235},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":236},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"真是年轻的话题。","id":238},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"怎么，您要给我一点“过来人的教诲”吗？","id":240},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":241},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"如果你允许我享受一下这种属于长辈的小小特权。","id":242},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","id":243},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"您请。","id":244},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"还记得八年前你对我说的话吗？","id":246},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......虽然我很不想破坏这么温情脉脉的气氛......","id":248},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$2","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"抱歉，阁下，真忘了。","id":250},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#3$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$2","focus":"1","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"你说的是，“不......我还有要做的事，要保护的人”。","id":252},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#3$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#11$2","focus":"2","id":253},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......听薇尔丽芙学我说话也太恶寒了。","id":254},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#11$2","focus":"1","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"......","id":256},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#6$1","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"彼时彼刻，你不愿让我替你做选择，此时此刻，你又何必要替菲亚梅塔做选择呢？","id":258},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":259},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"人的路总要自己去找，自己去选，自己去走。","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"薇尔，这也是给你的回答。","id":261},{"type":"Dialog","id":262},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":264},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":265},{"type":"Character","id":266},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g5_laterano_chapelout","screenadapt":"showall","id":267},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":268},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.4","id":269,"musicid":4},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":270},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":271},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......快到了，塞茜莉亚。","id":273},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"对不起，艾泽尔哥哥，我走得太慢了......太阳都快要落山了。","id":275},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"塞茜莉亚很了不起！毕竟没办法用公共交通......我们都走到移动地块以外啦。要是我有菲亚梅塔小姐的身手和力气，你也不用这么辛苦。","id":277},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"没关系的！其实妈妈也带我出来过，我们会走到离家很远的地方......和这里也差不多。","id":279},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"不过，菲亚梅塔姐姐不会发现我们偷偷来这里吗？","id":281},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"如果她只是查看终端的定位信号......希望我的花招至少能争取一点时间。","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"好在还是抵达了。","id":284},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"妈妈就是来了这里吗？","id":286},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":287},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......塞茜莉亚，我想了很久应该怎么和你解释这件事。","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"费莉亚......你的妈妈，确实来了这里，但她也不在这里。","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我没办法让你再见到妈妈。但在这里，你至少可以和她告别。","id":290},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥......你说的......我不太明白......","id":292},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"如果妈妈来了这里，又不在这里，那她是......又去了别的地方吗？","id":294},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"去了哪里呢？","id":295},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......我们先进去吧。","id":297},{"type":"Dialog","id":298},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":299},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":300},{"type":"Character","id":301},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g6_laterano_chapelin","screenadapt":"showall","id":302},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":303},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":304},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":305},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_368_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉特兰市民","text":"......父亲去世之前，一直希望他的葬礼上只有欢笑，不要有泪水，可我却......","id":307},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_368_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的修士","text":"我想，令尊真正希望的是，您不因他的离去陷入无法自拔的悲伤。","id":309},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的修士","text":"哭泣也好，欢笑也好，如果那就是您的道别......想必他都会欣然接受的。","id":310},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_368_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉特兰市民","text":"谢谢你......修士小姐......","id":312},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_368_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":313},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温和的修士","text":"我陪您去外面的花田走走吧。","id":314},{"type":"dialog","id":315},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":316},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":317},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":318},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥，那个姐姐说她的父亲也“去世”了......","id":320},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"嗯......去世的人，就会来到这里。","id":322},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"活着的人，在这里与他们道别......然后，带着对去世之人的思念，继续自己的生活。","id":323},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":324},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"那去世的人呢，他们做什么？","id":325},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":326},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......也许会在天上看着我们吧。","id":327},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":328},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"因为去了天上，所以再也见不到了吗？","id":329},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":330},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......","id":331},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":332},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"塞茜莉亚，给你。","id":333},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":334},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"这是......妈妈的守护铳？","id":335},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"嗯。","id":337},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我的爸爸妈妈，都是公证所的执行者。小时候我很少能见到他们......是爷爷把我带大的。","id":338},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":339},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"爷爷很喜欢他的铳，每次擦铳的时候，都会和我讲起他年轻时的事......","id":340},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"他参加过的战役，他的战友，他怎么遇到奶奶，还有我爸爸小时候的糗事......","id":341},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"看到爷爷的铳，我就会想起他讲的那些故事。","id":342},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......后来，爷爷去世了。我那时也只比你现在大一点点。","id":344},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"公证所的执行者，带走了他的守护铳。","id":345},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"就像你母亲的守护铳，本应被我带走。","id":346},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":347},{"type":"dialog","id":348},{"type":"character","id":349},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":350},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"$distressed_loop","volume":"0.4","id":351,"musicid":5},{"type":"Text","text":"艾泽尔缓缓蹲下，将费莉亚的铳放在塞茜莉亚手中。","id":352},{"type":"Text","text":"塞茜莉亚低下头，看着手中母亲的守护铳。","id":353},{"type":"Text","text":"艾泽尔轻轻握住塞茜莉亚的手。","id":354},{"type":"Text","text":"温热的水滴跌落在守护铳的浮雕花纹上，流到年幼女孩的掌心，堆积成一小片水渍。","id":355},{"type":"dialog","id":356},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":357},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":358},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥......我怎么哭了......","id":359},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":360},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我按爷爷教我的，每周给后院的盆栽浇水，后来它们开花了，我很高兴，喊爷爷来看。","id":361},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":362},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"喊出声才想起来，爷爷已经不在了。","id":363},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我再也见不到爷爷，再也没见过他的铳。","id":364},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"死亡就是永不再会的离别。","id":365},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#7$1","id":366},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......","id":367},{"type":"dialog","id":368},{"type":"character","id":369},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":370},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.7","fadetime":"2","id":371},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":372},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"然而离别本身即是对死亡的克服。","id":373},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"存者在此，去者在彼，才有“离别”。","id":374},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"“离别”是生者对逝者的惦念，也因此成为逝者存在的证明。","id":375},{"type":"dialog","id":376},{"type":"character","id":377},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":378},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":379},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":380},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"修士","text":"这就是为何我们需要道别。","id":381},{"type":"Dialog","id":382},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":383},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":384},{"type":"Dialog","id":385},{"type":"Character","id":386},{"type":"Image","id":387}],"characters":["艾泽尔","菲亚梅塔","愉快的小贩","安静的小贩","塞茜莉亚","？？？","薇尔丽芙","莫斯提马","教宗","拉特兰市民","温和的修士","修士"]}